# Hotel Management System

## Overview

This project is a Hotel Management System developed using MySQL. It demonstrates the design and implementation of a relational database for managing hotel operations, including customers, rooms, bookings, payments, and hotel services.

The project was created as part of my database learning journey to strengthen my SQL and database design skills.


## Features

- Customer Management
- Room Management
- Booking Management
- SQL Queries and Reports
- Database Relationships
- Data Analysis using SQL


## Database Tables

- Customers
- Rooms
- Bookings
- Employees
- Services
- Payments
- Invoices

---

